---
description: Testing patterns for Portfolio Kayro Gomes
globs: ["**/*.test.{ts,tsx}", "vitest.config.ts"]
---
- Test framework: Vitest with jsdom environment
- React component testing: @testing-library/react
- DOM assertions: @testing-library/jest-dom/vitest
- Setup file: `src/test/setup.ts`
- Colocate tests with source: `Component.test.tsx` next to `Component.tsx`
- Data tests: validate structure of `site.ts` and `projects.ts` exports
- Route tests: verify route configuration in `routes.ts`
- Run `npm run test` before committing
- Run `npm run test:coverage` for coverage report